                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18371211-name-378" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18371211-name-378" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371211-name-378" type="surname" value="HODGES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371211-name-378" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD HODGES</persName>
                  </hi>. I was drinking in the tap-room of the White Lion, between eight and nine o'clock, on the 10th of December—the prisoner was on my right-hand side—I had this bundle with me containing all these things—I missed it when I was told of it—I did not see the prisoner go out, but I missed him when I was told of it—the bundle was brought back to me—this is mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did you not give me the bundle? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> No, I did not.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. It was by the side of me, and he kept <hi rend="italic">shoving</hi> it towards me</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183712110064"></xptr>
               <p>—I said Do not push it to me"—he said "You may have it if you like. "</p>
